Job Details
A large real estate developer of mixed use projects wishes to appoint an experienced resource to facilitate the development and the strategy for the new development initiatives that this large semi government entity wishes to undertake.
Requirements
The candidate will be responsible for undertaking the feasibility of projects, appraising new development opportunities and reviewing existing developments, formulating a development plan that incorporates all strategies to be implemented and managing the relationships with banks and government authorities. The ideal candidate will be an MBA with at least seven years experience in the real estate industry in development and strategy and with an understanding of property management and development, cost control, quality and meeting time lines. To apply, please log onto our website: http//www.lobo management.com and mention Job Category: Real Estate/Property /Job Ref. No. LOBO/4174 /2014. Alternatively, email:  services@lobomanagement.com
